# ViralBoost AI - Website Functions and Systems (Web Info)

Is file me website ke pure functions, systems, aur capabilities simple Hinglish me diye gaye hain.

---

## 1) Website Kya Hai

ViralBoost AI ek creator + agency focused SaaS platform hai jo video content ko analyze, optimize, plan, aur monitor karne me help karta hai.

Primary goal:
- better content decisions
- higher viral potential
- faster workflow
- data-driven growth

---

## 2) Core User Functions (Website Kya Kar Sakti Hai)

### A) User Authentication and Account
- Email/password signup-login
- Unique ID + PIN login
- OTP based verification
- Forgot/reset password
- JWT based sessions
- Role-based access (user, manager, admin, super-admin)

### B) Video Input and Analysis
- Direct video upload
- YouTube/Facebook/Instagram/TikTok URL analysis
- Viral probability score
- Hook score, thumbnail score, title score
- Optimized title suggestions
- SEO description generation
- Tags and hashtags generation
- Best posting time recommendation

### C) YouTube Upload System
- Video upload to YouTube from dashboard
- Privacy selection (public/unlisted/private)
- Thumbnail upload
- SEO description + tags autofill (title based)
- Modeled viral-fit copy generation (SEO-oriented)
- Channel selection support:
  - default Google connected account
  - linked YouTube channels me se select karke upload

### D) YouTube Authentication and Channel Management
- Google OAuth connect
- Multiple channel connect flow
- Connected channels list
- Channel-wise token usage for upload
- Token refresh and save
- Channel disconnect support

### E) SEO + Discovery Tools
- YouTube SEO tools
- Keyword ideas
- Title score tools
- Description suggestions
- Hashtag tools
- Trending topic support
- Competitor context based optimization

### F) Analytics and Insights
- Dashboard analytics overview
- Growth and performance trends
- Engagement style insights
- Heatmap/best-time style outputs
- Analysis history and video-level details

### G) Calendar and Scheduling
- Content planning and schedule endpoints
- Calendar-based posting workflow

### H) Export and Reporting
- Analytics export support (CSV/Excel/PDF routes)
- White-label ready report inputs (company name/logo fields)

### I) Support and Communication
- Support tickets
- AI-assisted support response paths
- Chat session + message history

### J) API and Integrations
- API key management
- Public usage endpoint
- Webhook support for analysis events

